content:
This build was released on the 4th of August, 2021.
There are no differences between the Mario and Luigi versions of this build.

New areas:
Course 8 Area 3: Scary Sewer Maze
Wing Cap Area 3: Checkerboard 4
Bowser 2 Area 2: [Cryptic Hideout] (copy?)
Bowser 2 Area 3: Cryptic Hideout (warped)
Bowser 2 Area 4: Cryptic Hideout [crashma]

This verion also introduces the first jumpscare of the hack, Faceless Mario.
